---
---

<section id="chi-siamo" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-crema-chiaro">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Illustrazione decorativa -->
      <div class="reveal-left relative order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="relative aspect-square max-w-md mx-auto">
          <!-- Cerchio decorativo di sfondo -->
          <div class="absolute inset-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-crema to-ambra/15"></div>

          <!-- Icona centrale grande -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-48 h-48 sm:w-56 sm:h-56 bg-caffe-scuro rounded-3xl rotate-3 flex items-center justify-center shadow-xl">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="96" height="96" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-ambra">
                <path d="M17 8h1a4 4 0 1 1 0 8h-1"/>
                <path d="M3 8h14v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H7a4 4 0 0 1-4-4Z"/>
                <line x1="6" x2="6" y1="2" y2="4"/>
                <line x1="10" x2="10" y1="2" y2="4"/>
                <line x1="14" x2="14" y1="2" y2="4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Elementi decorativi flottanti -->
          <div class="absolute top-6 right-8 w-16 h-16 bg-ambra/20 rounded-2xl rotate-12 chi-float"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-6 w-12 h-12 bg-caffe-medio/15 rounded-full chi-float-delay"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-4 w-8 h-8 bg-crema rounded-lg -rotate-6 chi-float"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testo -->
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
        <div class="reveal-up">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ambra bg-ambra/10 rounded-full mb-4">
            Chi siamo
          </span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="reveal-up font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-caffe-scuro leading-tight">
          Passione e qualità<br>al tuo servizio
        </h2>

        <div class="reveal-up mt-6 space-y-4 text-testo-chiaro leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg">
          <p>
            Da anni ci occupiamo della <strong class="text-caffe-scuro">gestione completa di distributori automatici</strong> per uffici, aziende e spazi pubblici. La nostra missione è semplice: offrire un servizio puntuale, prodotti di qualità e la tranquillità di un'assistenza sempre disponibile.
          </p>
          <p>
            Dalla scelta del distributore più adatto al rifornimento costante, dalla manutenzione ordinaria all'assistenza tecnica rapida — ci prendiamo cura di ogni dettaglio perché tu possa goderti la tua pausa caffè senza pensieri.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Punti di forza -->
        <div class="reveal-up mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ambra/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-ambra"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-caffe-scuro text-sm">Installazione gratuita</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ambra/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-ambra"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-caffe-scuro text-sm">Rifornimento costante</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ambra/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-ambra"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-caffe-scuro text-sm">Assistenza rapida</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ambra/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-ambra"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-caffe-scuro text-sm">Prodotti selezionati</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="reveal-up mt-10">
          <a
            href="/contatti"
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-ambra font-semibold hover:text-ambra-hover transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            Scopri di più su di noi
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @reference "../../styles/global.css";

  .chi-float {
    animation: chiFloat 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .chi-float-delay {
    animation: chiFloat 8s ease-in-out 1.5s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes chiFloat {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(var(--tw-rotate, 0deg)); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px) rotate(var(--tw-rotate, 0deg)); }
  }
</style>